UleRobots TEAM

This is a simple talker node that publishes
std_msgs/String to the /chatter topic and a listener node that subscribes 
to these messages.

We have used a simple cypher method for this example.
http://www.laurentluce.com/posts/python-and-cryptography-with-pycrypto/

-------------------------------------------------------

The key element trick is to apply pycrypto

sudo apt-get install python-pip
sudo apt-get install autoconf g++ python2.7-dev
sudo apt-get install python-devel
pip  install pycrypto


~/tmp$ pip show pycrypto
---
Name: pycrypto
Version: 2.6.1
Location: /usr/lib/python2.7/dist-packages
Requires: 

